{"tid":1641854,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"起初，黑警抓商場保安的時候， 我沉默了，因為我不是商場保安。","createTime":"2019-10-09T13:09:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T04:48:46.000Z","uid":90601,"like":129,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"a3d162c14352808a46f24ae34a761b0f5dcd737a","tid":1641854,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:09:40.000Z","msg":"起初，納粹抓共產黨人的時候，<br />\n我沉默了，因為我不是共產黨人。<br />\n<br />\n當他們抓社會民主主義者的時候，<br />\n我沉默了，因為我不是社會民主主義者。<br />\n<br />\n當他們抓工會成員的時候，<br />\n我沉默了，因為我不是工會成員。<br />\n<br />\n當他們抓猶太人的時候，<br />\n我沉默了，因為我不是猶太人。<br />\n<br />\n最後當他們來抓我時，<br />\n再也沒有人站起來為我說話了。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n今次保安單野，一定要想令五位盡責既保安知道，全香港人都支持佢地<br />\n眾籌又好，聲援又好，一定唔可以由得佢<br />\n<br />\n黑警就想捉曬所有見義勇為既人<br />\n令之後無人敢反抗佢地，佢地可以為所欲為"},{"pid":"ce33c0611ba9e2832cd93370b7281c87a2ee8905","tid":1641854,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:10:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a8d8439923eb6b4faf9b6fe35cdbc9e27332dc","tid":1641854,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:10:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"318f1980aa10b6ec06fa17676630d0c1b1b08784","tid":1641854,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:10:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b825f1d8bb9f8aaed43bab5c37103f2c9347e3d"